#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:5
msgid "Fly/Walk Mode"
msgstr "飞行/行走模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:7
msgid ""
"There are cases where it's preferable to navigate with first person controls, "
"especially for large environments such as architectural models. In these cases "
"orbiting around the view center is limiting. While zoom, pan & dolly can be "
"used, it's inconvenient."
msgstr ""
"在某些情况下，最好使用第一人称控制视角漫游，尤其是对于大型环境，如建筑模型。 在"
"这些情况下，围绕视图中心的视轨作用有限。 虽然可以使用缩放、平移和滑动，但这很不"
"方便。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:12
msgid ""
"With walk/fly modes you can navigate around the scene where view rotation is "
"performed from the cameras location."
msgstr ""
"使用行走/飞行模式，可以在场景中各处漫游，并会从相机位置旋转视角(译者注：以视图"
"相机为视角旋转中心)。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:17
msgid "View Navigation."
msgstr "视图漫游。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:19
msgid ""
"In the :doc:`Preferences editor </editors/preferences/index>` select the "
"navigation mode you want to use as default when invoking the View Navigation "
"operator. Alternatively you can call the individual modes from the View "
"Navigation menu."
msgstr ""
"在 :doc:`偏好设置编辑器 </editors/preferences/index>` 中，选择要在调用视图漫游"
"操作时默认使用的漫游模式。 或者，可以从视图漫游菜单中调用各个模式。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:23
msgid "Common use cases for walk/fly include:"
msgstr "行走/飞行常见用例包括："

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:25
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "漫游"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:26
msgid "This can be a quick way to navigate a large scene."
msgstr "这可以是漫游大型场景的快捷方式。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:27
msgid "Camera Placement"
msgstr "相机机位"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:28
msgid "When activated from a camera view, this will move the camera too."
msgstr "当相机视图激活时，这也会移动摄像机。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:32
msgid "Recording Animation"
msgstr "录制动画"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:30
msgid ""
"Running from a camera with auto-keyframe and playing animation will record the "
"motion as you make it allowing you to record the walk-through."
msgstr "移动具有自动关键帧和播放动画功能的相机将记录运动，允许记录走过的场景。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:37
msgid "Walk Mode"
msgstr "行走模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:39
#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:82
msgid "Reference"
msgstr "参考"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst
msgid "Mode"
msgstr "模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:42
#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:85
msgid "All modes"
msgstr "所有模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst
msgid "Hotkey"
msgstr "快捷键"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:43
#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:86
msgid ":kbd:`Shift-AccentGrave`"
msgstr ":kbd:`Shift-AccentGrave`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst
msgid "Menu"
msgstr "菜单"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:44
msgid ":menuselection:`View --> Navigation --> Walk Navigation`"
msgstr ""
":menuselection:`视图(View) --> 漫游(Navigation) --> 行走漫游(Walk Navigation)`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:46
msgid ""
"On activation the mouse pointer will move at the center of the view, and a "
"cross marker will appear..."
msgstr "在激活时，鼠标指针会移动到视图的中心， 并且会出现十字准星标记……"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:49
msgid ""
"This navigation mode behaves similar to the first person navigation system "
"available in most 3D world games. It works with a combination of keyboard "
"arrow keys and mouse movement."
msgstr ""
"该漫游模式的行为类似于大多数3D世界游戏中可用的第一人称漫游系统。 它结合使用键盘"
"箭头键和鼠标移动。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:54
#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:94
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "快捷键"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:56
msgid "Move the mouse in the direction you want to look."
msgstr "移动鼠标调整视角。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:57
msgid ""
"Arrow keys or :kbd:`W`, :kbd:`A`, :kbd:`S`, :kbd:`D` move forwards/backwards "
"and strafe left/right."
msgstr "箭头键或 :kbd:`W`， :kbd:`S`， :kbd:`A`， :kbd:`D` 前后移动和左右挪动。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:58
msgid "Teleport :kbd:`Spacebar`."
msgstr "传送 :kbd:`Spacebar` 。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:60
msgid ""
"This moves you to the location at the cross-hair (offset by the *camera "
"height* value set in the :doc:`Preferences </editors/preferences/index>`)."
msgstr ""
"这会将相机移动到十字准线的位置(偏移值由 :doc:`偏好设置 </editors/preferences/"
"index>` 中设置的 *视角高度* 值确定)。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:62
msgid "Jump :kbd:`V` -- only in *gravity* mode."
msgstr "跳跃 :kbd:`V` ——仅 *重力* 模式下。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:63
msgid "Move up and down :kbd:`Q`, :kbd:`E` -- only in *free* mode."
msgstr "上下移动 :kbd:`Q` ， :kbd:`E` ——仅 *自由* 模式下。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:64
msgid "Alternate between *free* and *gravity* modes :kbd:`Tab`."
msgstr "使用 :kbd:`Tab` 在 *自由* 和 *重力* 模式之间切换。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:65
msgid "Change the movement speed:"
msgstr "改变移动速度："

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:67
msgid ""
":kbd:`WheelUp` or :kbd:`NumpadPlus` to increase the movement speed for this "
"open session."
msgstr ":kbd:`WheelUp` 或 :kbd:`NumpadPlus` 增加此次开启的会话中的移动速度。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:68
msgid ""
":kbd:`WheelDown` or :kbd:`NumpadMinus` to decrease the movement speed for this "
"open session."
msgstr ":kbd:`WheelDown` 或 :kbd:`NumpadMinus` 减小此次开启的会话中的移动速度。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:69
msgid ":kbd:`Shift` (hold) -- to speed up the movement temporarily."
msgstr ":kbd:`Shift` (按住)——暂时加速运动。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:70
msgid ":kbd:`Alt` (hold) -- to slow down the movement temporarily."
msgstr ":kbd:`Alt` (按住)——暂时减速运动。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:72
#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:114
msgid ""
"When you are happy with the new view, click :kbd:`LMB` to confirm. In case you "
"want to go back from where you started, press :kbd:`Esc` or :kbd:`RMB`, as "
"usual."
msgstr ""
"当对新视图感到满意后，按 :kbd:`LMB` 确认。按下 :kbd:`Esc` 或 :kbd:`RMB` ，返回"
"初始位置。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:75
msgid ""
"If the defaults values (speed, mouse sensitivity, ...) need adjustments for "
"your project, in the :doc:`Preferences </editors/preferences/index>` you can "
"select a few options for the navigation system:"
msgstr ""
"如果要为项目调整默认值(速度，鼠标敏感性……)，可以到 :doc:`偏好设置 </editors/"
"preferences/index>` 中调整相关选项："

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:80
msgid "Fly Mode"
msgstr "飞行模式"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:87
msgid ":menuselection:`View --> Navigation --> Fly Navigation`"
msgstr ""
":menuselection:`视图(View) --> 漫游(Navigation) --> 飞行漫游(Fly Navigation)`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:89
msgid ""
"On activation the cursor is centered inside a rectangle that defines a safe-"
"region. When the cursor is outside this region the view will rotate/pan."
msgstr ""
"激活时，光标位于定义为安全区块的矩形中心。 当光标位于此区块之外时，视图将旋转/"
"平移。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:96
msgid "Move the mouse outside the safe-region in the direction you want to look."
msgstr "将鼠标沿着想要查看的方向，移动到安全区块之外。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:97
msgid "Move the view forward/backward:"
msgstr "前后移动视图相机："

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:99
msgid ":kbd:`WheelUp` or :kbd:`NumpadPlus` to accelerate the movement forward."
msgstr ":kbd:`WheelUp` 或 :kbd:`NumpadPlus` 加速向前移动。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:100
msgid ""
":kbd:`WheelDown` or :kbd:`NumpadMinus` to accelerate the movement backward."
msgstr ":kbd:`WheelDown` 或 :kbd:`NumpadMinus` 加速向后移动。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:102
msgid ""
"So if the view is already moving forward, :kbd:`WheelDown`, :kbd:`NumpadMinus` "
"will eventually stop it and then move it backward, etc."
msgstr ""
"因此，如果视图正在向前移动， :kbd:`WheelDown` ， :kbd:`NumpadMinus` 会将其停"
"住，然后向后移动, 等等。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:104
msgid ":kbd:`MMB` Drag to pan the view."
msgstr ":kbd:`MMB` 拖动平移视图相机。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:106
msgid ""
"In this case the view can move laterally on its local axis at the moment you "
"drag the mouse."
msgstr "在这种情况下，在拖动鼠标时，视图相机可以在其局部轴上横向移动。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:107
msgid ":kbd:`Shift` precision (slow the momentum)."
msgstr ":kbd:`Shift` 刹车模式(减慢变动)。"

# 限制视图相机轨迹可能更合适，乘客模式？
#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:108
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl` disable rotation."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl` 乘客模式(视图相机转动不影响其运动)。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/walk_fly.rst:110
msgid ""
"While held, the view rotation doesn't influence the flight direction, this "
"allows you to fly past an object, keeping it centered in the view, even as you "
"fly away from it."
msgstr ""
"保持时，视图相机旋转不会影响飞行方向，这使您可以飞过一个物体，使其在视图中保持"
"居中，即使您飞离它也是如此。"
